19std::unique_ptr<VideoStreamDecoderInterface> CreateVideoStreamDecoder(
20 VideoStreamDecoderInterface::Callbacks* callbacks,
21 VideoDecoderFactory* decoder_factory,
22 TaskQueueFactory* task_queue_factory,
23 std::map<int, std::pair<SdpVideoFormat, int>> decoder_settings) {
